<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MATCH TEAM - Gaming Community</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/transition.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/header.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #ff1f6d;
            --secondary-color: #4169e1;
            --background-color: #0a0d1c;
            --text-color: #ffffff;
            --gold-color: #ffd700;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--background-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .logo-img {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .logo span {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .auth-buttons, .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .box {
            width: 150px;
            height: 50px;
            transition: 1s linear;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: center;
            background: transparent;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 900;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .box:before {
            position: absolute;
            content: '';
            left: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            height: 4px;
            width: 100%;
            border-bottom: 4px solid transparent;
            border-left: 4px solid transparent;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transform: translateX(100%);
        }

        .box:after {
            position: absolute;
            content: '';
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            border-top: 4px solid transparent;
            border-right: 4px solid transparent;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transform: translateX(-100%);
        }

        .box:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 255, 117, 0.3);
        }

        .box:hover:before {
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
            height: 100%;
            transform: translateX(0);
            transition: .6s transform linear, .6s height linear .6s;
        }

        .box:hover:after {
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
            height: 100%;
            transform: translateX(0);
            transition: .6s transform linear, .6s height linear 1s;
        }

        .book-btn {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            outline: none;
            border: none;
            background: transparent;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            font-size: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            transition: 0.6s ease;
        }

        .box:hover .book-btn {
            color: var(--background-color);
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
        }

        main {
            flex-grow: 1;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .content {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .text-content {
            flex: 1;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        h2 {
            color: var(--gold-color);
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .star-container {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .star-bg {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.5;
            position: absolute;
        }

        .star {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            fill: var(--primary-color);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .wave {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100px;
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            opacity: 0.3;
            border-top-left-radius: 100% 100%;
            border-top-right-radius: 100% 100%;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .content {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .star-container {
                order: -1;
            }

            .star-bg, .star {
                width: 200px;
                height: 200px;
            }
        }

        .box.white-btn {
            border: 1px solid var(--text-color);
        }

        .box.white-btn .book-btn {
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

        .box.white-btn:hover .book-btn {
            color: var(--background-color);
            background-color: var(--text-color);
        }

        .box.white-btn:hover:before,
        .box.white-btn:hover:after {
            border-color: var(--text-color);
        }

        header .box {
            width: 130px;
            height: 40px;
        }

        header .book-btn {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <%- include('partials/header', {currentPage: 'index',isLoggedIn: true,is_admin: false, username: 'اسم المستخدم',profilePicture: '/path/to/profile/picture.jpg' }) %>
    <main>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="text-content">
                <h1>DETOXIFY YOUR GAME</h1>
                <h2>ابحث عن مباراتك المفضلة</h2>
                <p>انضم إلى مجتمعنا حيث يمكنك حجز تذاكر مبارياتك المفضلة بسهولة وأمان. سجل الآن وابدأ رحلتك في عالم كرة القدم المثير.</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <div class="box">
                        <a href="/matches" class="book-btn">هيا نبدأ</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="box white-btn">
                        <a href="/about" class="book-btn">اعرف المزيد</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="star-container">
                <div class="star-bg"></div>
                <svg class="star" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2" />
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <div class="wave"></div>
   
    <script>
        // منع ظهور المحتوى قبل تحميل الـ JavaScript
        document.body.style.opacity = '0';
        window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            document.body.style.opacity = '1';
        });
    </script> <script src="/scripts/transition.js"></script>

</body>
</html>